Package edu.brown.cs.mramesh4.Graph

Interface GraphEdge<N extends GraphNode<N,​E>,​E extends GraphEdge<N,​E>>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - representing the type of node to be used in the Graph class.
    E - representing the type of edge to be used in the Graph class.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Way
    public interface GraphEdge<N extends GraphNode<N,​E>,​E extends GraphEdge<N,​E>>
    This interface allows generic edges to be used in our Graph class for the A* search. It defines some common methods that all edges should implement.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      N getFrom()
      This method returns the Node that is at the start of the current edge.
      N getTo()
      This method returns the Node that is at the end of the current edge.
      double getWeight()
      This method returns the weight, or distance, of the current edge.
